\begin_layout Section*
Chapter 1: preference and choice
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
1.B.1
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Since 
\begin_inset Formula $\succsim$
\end_inset

 is rational, it must satisfy transitivity.
 Hence, For all x, y, z , if 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim y$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $y\succsim z$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim z$
\end_inset

.
 And because 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succ y\succsim z$
\end_inset

, we have 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim y\succsim z$
\end_inset

.
 So we get 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim z$
\end_inset

.
 Now we need to prove that 
\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none

\begin_inset Formula $x\precsim z$
\end_inset

 is impossible.

\family default
\series default
\shape default
\size default
\emph default
\bar default
\strikeout default
\uuline default
\uwave default
\noun default
\color inherit
 If 
\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none

\begin_inset Formula $x\precsim z$
\end_inset

, then because of
\family default
\series default
\shape default
\size default
\emph default
\bar default
\strikeout default
\uuline default
\uwave default
\noun default
\color inherit
 transitivity, we have
\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none
 
\begin_inset Formula $y\succsim x$
\end_inset

.
 But this contradicts with 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succ y$
\end_inset

.
 
\family default
\series default
\shape default
\size default
\emph default
\bar default
\strikeout default
\uuline default
\uwave default
\noun default
\color inherit
Hence, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succ z$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
1.B.2
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $y\succ x\Leftrightarrow y\succsim x$
\end_inset

 but not 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim y$
\end_inset

.
 we cannot have 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim x$
\end_inset

 but not 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim x$
\end_inset

 at the same time.
 Hence 
\begin_inset Formula $\succ$
\end_inset

is irreflexive.
 And 
\end_layout

